@{
    TempData["Title"] = "Bootstrap 4 Buttons & Button Groups";
}

<h1 class="py-2 px-5 mb-0">@TempData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="container">
    <h2>Button Styles</h2>
    <p>Bootstrap 4 provides different styles of buttons:</p>

    <button type="button" class="btn" onclick="swal.fire('I am a Basic button.')">Basic</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="swal.fire('I am a Primary button.')">Primary</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="swal.fire('I am a Secondary button.')">Secondary</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-success" onclick="swal.fire('I am a Success button.')">Success</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-info" onclick="swal.fire('BaI am a Info button.sic')">Info</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning" onclick="swal.fire('I am a Warning button.')">Warning</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" onclick="swal.fire('I am a Danger button.')">Danger</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-dark" onclick="swal.fire('I am a Dark button.')">Dark</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-light" onclick="swal.fire('I am a Light button.')">Light</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-link" onclick="swal.fire('I am a Link button.')">Link</button>

    <h3 class="mt-2">Block Level Buttons</h3>
    <p>Nest button groups to create dropdown menus:</p>

    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Button 1</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-block">Button 2</button>

    <h3 class="mt-2">Large Block Level Buttons</h3>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block">Button 1</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-lg btn-block">Button 2</button>

    <h3 class="mt-2">Small Block Level Buttons</h3>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm btn-block">Button 1</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-sm btn-block">Button 2</button>

    <hr />
</div>

<div class="container">
    <h2 class="mt-2">Button group</h2>
    <p>Group a series of buttons together on a single line with the button group, and super-power them with JavaScript.</p>

    <div class="btn-group" role="group">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary">Left</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary">Middle</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary">Right</button>
    </div>

    <div class="btn-group" role="group">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary">on</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary">off</button>
    </div>

    <h3 class="mt-2">Nesting Button Groups</h3>
    <p>Nest button groups to create dropdown menus:</p>

    <div class="btn-group">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Apple</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Samsung</button>
        <div class="btn-group">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown">
                Sony
            </button>
            <div class="dropdown-menu">
                <a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Tablet</a>
                <a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Smartphone</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr />
</div>

<div class="container">
    <h2>Button toolbar</h2>
    <p>Combine sets of button groups into button toolbars for more complex components. Use utility classes as needed to space out groups, buttons, and more.</p>

    <div class="btn-toolbar" role="toolbar" aria-label="Toolbar with button groups">
        <div class="btn-group mr-2" role="group" aria-label="First group">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary">1</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary">2</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary">3</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary">4</button>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-group mr-2" role="group" aria-label="Second group">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary">5</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary">6</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary">7</button>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-group" role="group" aria-label="Third group">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary">8</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr />
</div>
